name: Auto SlilentMe
shortDescription: Forgot each time when you walk into a meeting room and silent your device? Embarrassed when your device rings and everybody stares at you in the middle of a discussion? Well then this little tweak is for you!! Just install it then leave the rest to it. Works tightly with your calendar application and silent (reduce the noice till the very minimum level) your device based on your meetings in the calendar.
author: IArrays
